Important outcome

The biggest shift today is that the repo became more explicit about how typed surfaces, retrieval paths, and generated outputs are supposed to work.

Flow Builder is no longer just a loose surface concept. It now has a typed-surface contract, a token-domain map, and an application note that make the intended boundaries easier to preserve.

